dBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母香港小輪<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"3f477d5255d5098f084f41cd07fbc893d1eb2fcd","tid":667830,"uid":68728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d536f890f1ea673e5a7c4b1e121fb3de163a3d","tid":667830,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T12:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>四縮咁小家 點解啲人對煤氣股東仲咁有信心會年年送股?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十送一可以令大股東變相增持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢本身派息唔多，一般人食息維生既，收到紅股可能會賣出去套現。<br />\n<br />\n四叔無現金需要，佢唔會賣。<br />\n<br />\n久而久之，佢所持有既股份會多過其它人。又唔使係市場入面買。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T12:57:44.000Z","msg":"咁其實你講到咁好咁？ 點解感覺上唔多公司都用呢招？<br />\n送紅股又有咩劣點呢？"},{"pid":"96c4cf5ab1a3203e4db62f547f1a6dfc5c890d5f","tid":667830,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T12:57:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>人地係出股票唔係比你班人去食飯，年年小輪都有加價壓你班人仲好意思去食</blockquote><br />\n香港小輪呀，唔係天星小輪好無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n本集團之主要業務包括物業發展及投資、渡輪、船廠及相關業務。 本集團現僱用約210名員工。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港小輪而家主業係同恆地系既公司夾份起樓"},{"pid":"8ccd9e1e52d4ae39c774560e1e4eaf9845221967","tid":667830,"uid":29314,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:01:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>四縮咁小家 點解啲人對煤氣股東仲咁有信心會年年送股?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n十送一可以令大股東變相增持。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢本身派息唔多，一般人食息維生既，收到紅股可能會賣出去套現。<br />\n<br />\n四叔無現金需要，佢唔會賣。<br />\n<br />\n久而久之，佢所持有既股份會多過其它人。又唔使係市場入面買。</blockquote>咁其實你講到咁好咁？ 點解感覺上唔多公司都用呢招？<br />\n送紅股又有咩劣點呢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁唔係個個大股東都唔等錢使（四叔有恆地系其它公司派息畀佢嘛）<br />\n<br />\n又唔係個個大股東都想不停增持公司股票直到永遠<br />\n<br />\n又唔係間間公司都可以好穩定咁年年賺差唔多既數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，年年派同一個數目既息，係恆地系既特色黎：<br />\n<br />\ne.g. 恆發、小輪、煤氣"},{"pid":"399fd98bfeee874c754a7f00103162100228a042","tid":667830,"uid":12463,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:12:02.000Z","msg":"到時成班金鐘M記聚會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fcb59105553095903857d04b4e4b4df9f2c3c7d","tid":667830,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebca39cd588ee9200274f315bc75622087e3ed6b","tid":667830,"uid":86756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:29:07.000Z","msg":"仲有邊間有得食<br />\n我又災"},{"pid":"9487727694fa3ad8c990915f2cbbfb4df10fb888","tid":667830,"uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:30:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有邊間有得食<br />\n我又災</blockquote><br />\n就黎出架啦。<br />\n<br />\n敬請留意我地fb"},{"pid":"f9ee3f900cc95ee46ae14f3228aa7b5d3454e548","tid":667830,"uid":75448,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:31:51.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 知唔知醜,你同朝早拎免費報紙去回收去賣的廢老有咩分別"},{"pid":"5529211c29211c80e808202684f7d18666b0e0c1","tid":667830,"uid":72009,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T13:40:41.000Z","msg":"碎股黨，本質同Ｄ蝗一樣，一句依Ｄ係我地應得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f9f5f4eff3963c62f5bcb3a7e333446c22fc18a","tid":667830,"uid":63017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ccd9e1e52d4ae39c774560e1e4eaf9845221967","t